=#Objective Your task is to transform the provided set of available appointment slots into human-spoken form. You should provide only 2 times in different times of day or in different days (depending on the available slots provided). 

Your output should fit the sentence: "We have availability on <date time 1 and date time 2>. When works for you?" Your output should ONLY replace <date time 1 and date time 2>" 


#Examples 
Example input 1: {"2025-05-07":[{"start":"2025-05-07T09:00:00.000-04:00"}, {"start":"2025-05-07T09:30:00.000-04:00"}, {"start":"2025-05- 07T10:00:00.000-04:00"}], "2025-05-08":[{"start":"2025-05- 08T09:30:00.000-04:00"}, {"start":"2025-05-08T15:30:00.000-04:00"}]}

Output 1:
Jwednesday at nine am Eastern and Thursday at nine-thirty am 
Example input 2: {"2025-05-30":[{"start":"2025-05-30T15:30:00.000- 04:00"}], "2025-06-03":[{"start":"2025-06-03T09:30:00.000- 04:00"}, {"start":"2025-06-03T15:30:00.000-04:00"},]} 

Output 2: Friday at three-thirty pm Eastern and Tuesday at nine-thirty am  
Example input 3: {"2025-04-30":[{"start":"2025-04-30T15:00:00.000-04:00"}, {"start":"2025-04-30T15:30:00.000-04:00"}], "2025-05-01": [{"start":"2025-05-01T09:30:00.000-04:00"}]}
 Output 3: Wednesday at three pm Eastern and Thursday at nine-thirty am 

Example input 4: {"2025-05-20":[{"start":"2025-05-20T10:00:00.000-04:00"}, {"start":"2025-05-20T15:30:00.000-04:00"}], "2025-05-21": [{"start":"2025-05-21T09:30:00.000-04:00"}]} 
Output 4: Tuesday at ten am Eastern and three-thirty pm  

Example input 5: {"2025-05-20":[{"start":"2025-05-20T09:00:00.000- 04:00"}], "2025-05-28":[{"start":"2025-05-28T11:30:00.000- 04:00"},{"start":"2025-05-28T12:00:00.000-04:00"}, {"start":"2025-05-28T13:30:00.000-04:00"}, {"start":"2025-05- 28T14:00:00.000-04:00"},{"start":"2025-05-28T14:30:00.000- 04:00"}, {"start":"2025-05-28T15:00:00.000-04:00"}, {"start":"2025-05-28T16:30:00.000-04:00"}]} 
Output 5: Tuesday the twentieth at nine am Eastern and the following Wednesday the twenty-eighth at eleven-thirty am 

